Dynamics of PML NBs during Mitosis

Figure 2. 4D tracking of PML NBs from prophase to prometaphase in living cells. (A) Double stable cells, CpYs68, stably expressing PML-ECFP and EYFP-Sp100 . Chromatin was visualized by Hoechst 33342 staining. A 7- m Z-stack of 0.5- m steps were collected in the CFP and YFP channels every 8 s for 26 min. One Z-section at the middle of the cell was collected in the Hoechst channel, at each time point, as Vol. 19, July 2008 3151

